  "english": [
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>The</b> aforementioned <b>pepper mill</b> is a composite vessel, and each of its parts must be considered independently with respect to ritual impurity. It <b>is susceptible to ritual impurity because of</b> each of the <b>three vessels</b> of which it is comprised: It is susceptible to impurity <b>because</b> it is a wooden <b>receptacle,</b> it is susceptible to impurity <b>because</b> it is <b>a metal vessel, and</b> it is susceptible to impurity <b>because</b> it is <b>a sieve.</b>",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> A Sage <b>taught:</b> The <b>lower</b> section of the mill is susceptible to impurity <b>because</b> it is viewed as <b>a receptacle,</b> since the ground pepper descends into it. <b>The middle</b> section is susceptible to impurity <b>because</b> it is <b>a sieve,</b> as it serves to filter the pepper. Finally, the <b>upper</b> part, in which the pepper is actually ground, is susceptible to impurity <b>because</b> it is <b>a metal vessel.</b> Although it is not a receptacle, it is nevertheless susceptible to impurity, since it is made of metal.",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>A child’s wagon,</b> with which he plays and upon which he also sits, <b>is susceptible to ritual impurity</b> imparted by <b>treading.</b> It is considered a fixed seat of the child, so that if the child is a <i>zav</i> and he sits on the wagon, it contracts the ritual impurity imparted by the treading of a <i>zav</i>. <b>And</b> this wagon <b>may be handled on Shabbat,</b> as it is considered a vessel. <b>And it may be dragged</b> on the ground on Shabbat <b>only upon cloth,</b> a stone pavement, or the like, as otherwise it would create a furrow when dragged, and one would be liable due to the prohibited labor of plowing.",
    "<b>Rabbi Yehuda says:</b> For this reason, <b>no vessels may be dragged</b> on the ground on Shabbat <b>except for a wagon,</b> which is permitted <b>because</b> its wheels do not make a furrow in the ground but merely <b>press</b> the earth down. Since no earth is moved from its place, this is not considered digging or plowing on Shabbat.",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> It is taught in the mishna that <b>a child’s wagon is susceptible to ritual impurity</b> imparted by <b>treading.</b> Why? It is <b>because he leans on it.</b> The mishna also teaches that this wagon <b>may be handled on Shabbat.</b> Why? It is <b>because it has the status of a vessel,</b> and one may handle a vessel on Shabbat.",
    "The mishna further teaches that a child’s wagon <b>may be dragged</b> on Shabbat <b>only upon cloth.</b> The Gemara infers: <b>Upon cloth, yes,</b> it is permitted; but directly <b>on the ground, no,</b> it is not permitted. <b>What is the reason</b> for this <i>halakha</i>? It is <b>because he creates a furrow</b> in the ground when he drags the wagon across it. The Gemara asks: In accordance with <b>whose</b> opinion is this mishna? <b>It is</b> in accordance with the opinion of <b>Rabbi Yehuda, who said: An unintentional act,</b> i.e., a permitted action from which an unintended prohibited labor ensues on Shabbat, <b>is prohibited,</b> even though the person performing it does not have the prohibited labor in mind.",
    "<b>As, if</b> it were in accordance with the opinion of <b>Rabbi Shimon, didn’t he say: An unintentional act is permitted,</b> since there was no intention to perform the prohibited action? <b>As we learned</b> explicitly in a mishna that <b>Rabbi Shimon says: A person may drag a bed, a chair, or a bench</b> on the ground, <b>provided that he does not intend to make a furrow.</b> Even if one forms a furrow unwittingly, one need not be concerned, as this was not his intention.",
    "The Gemara raises a difficulty: If so, <b>say the latter clause</b> of the mishna as follows: <b>Rabbi Yehuda says: No vessels may be dragged</b> on the ground <b>on Shabbat except for a wagon, because it</b> merely <b>presses</b> the earth down. This is not prohibited as plowing because it does not create a furrow. This indicates that a wagon may be dragged on the ground on Shabbat <b>because, yes, it presses</b> the earth down, <b>but it does not make a furrow.</b> Since it has already been established that the first section of the mishna is also in accordance with the opinion of Rabbi Yehuda, and there it appears that a wagon dragged along the ground makes a furrow, Rabbi Yehuda seems to contradict himself.",
    "The Gemara answers: It must be explained that this is a dispute between <b>two <i>tanna’im</i></b> who hold <b>in accordance with</b> the opinion of <b>Rabbi Yehuda</b> but differ with regard to the content of that opinion. The first <i>tanna</i> holds that even a wagon makes a furrow, whereas the other <i>tanna</i> maintains in the name of Rabbi Yehuda that a wagon does not make a furrow.",
    "",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>One may not trap fish from</b> their <b>ponds on a Festival</b> even with the intention of eating them, as this falls into the category of hunting, a type of labor that is not permitted on a Festival. <b>Nor may one place food before them,</b> as it is not his duty to feed them; rather, they maintain themselves by eating smaller fish or different types of algae that grow in the water.",
    "<b>However, one may trap an animal or a bird from</b> their <b>enclosures [<i>beivarim</i>],</b> as they are viewed as already captured, and therefore the action is not considered an act of hunting. <b>And one may</b> also <b>place food before them</b> as one does for other household animals.",
    "<b>Rabban Shimon ben Gamliel says: Not all enclosures are identical</b> with respect to the <i>halakhot</i> of hunting. <b>This is the principle:</b> With regard to <b>any</b> animal"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"106\" data-sentence-id=\"0\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"א\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> הָרֵחַיִם שֶׁל פִּלְפְּלִין, טְמֵאָה מִשּׁוּם",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁלֹשָׁה כֵּלִים: מִשּׁוּם כְּלִי קִבּוּל, וּמִשּׁוּם כְּלִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַתֶּכֶת, וּמִשּׁוּם כְּלִי כְּבָרָה<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"119\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"107\" data-sentence-id=\"1\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ב\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> תָּנָא: תַּחְתּוֹנָה —",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִשּׁוּם כְּלִי קִבּוּל, אֶמְצָעִית — מִשּׁוּם",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּלִי כְּבָרָה, עֶלְיוֹנָה — מִשּׁוּם כְּלִי מַתֶּכֶת<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"120\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"108\" data-sentence-id=\"2\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ג\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> עֲגָלָה שֶׁל קָטָן — טְמֵאָה מִדְרָס,",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְנִטֶּלֶת בְּשַׁבָּת, וְאֵינָהּ נִגְרֶרֶת אֶלָּא עַל גַּבֵּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כֵלִים. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-121\" href=\"/beitzah/23b#gemara-line-8\" title=\"Mishnah source: Beitzah 23b\"><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span> אוֹמֵר: כׇּל הַכֵּלִים אֵין נִגְרָרִין,</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-121\" href=\"/beitzah/23b#gemara-line-8\" title=\"Mishnah source: Beitzah 23b\">חוּץ מִן הָעֲגָלָה, מִפְּנֵי שֶׁהִיא כּוֹבֶשֶׁת</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"121\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"109\" data-sentence-id=\"4\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ד\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> עֲגָלָה שֶׁל קָטָן — טְמֵאָה מִדְרָס, דְּהָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "סָמֵיךְ עִלָּוַיהּ. וְנִטֶּלֶת בְּשַׁבָּת, מִשּׁוּם דְּאִיכָּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תּוֹרַת כְּלִי עֲלַהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאֵינָהּ נִגְרֶרֶת אֶלָּא עַל גַּבֵּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כֵלִים. עַל גַּבֵּי כֵלִים — אִין, עַל גַּבֵּי קַרְקַע — לָא.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַאי טַעְמָא, דְּקָא עָבֵיד חָרִיץ. מַנִּי? <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הִיא, דְּאָמַר: דָּבָר שֶׁאֵין מִתְכַּוֵּין — אָסוּר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>דְּאִי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16403\">רַבִּי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16403\">שִׁמְעוֹן</span>, הָאָמַר: דָּבָר שֶׁאֵין מִתְכַּוֵּין — מוּתָּר.",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "(דִּתְנַן) <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">רַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span> אוֹמֵר: גּוֹרֵר אָדָם מִטָּה",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כִּסֵּא וְסַפְסָל, וּבִלְבַד שֶׁלֹּא יִתְכַּוֵּין לַעֲשׂוֹת",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חָרִיץ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֵימָא סֵיפָא, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span> אוֹמֵר: אֵין הַכֹּל",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נִגְרָרִין בְּשַׁבָּת, חוּץ מִן הָעֲגָלָה, מִפְּנֵי שֶׁהִיא",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כּוֹבֶשֶׁת. מִפְּנֵי שֶׁכּוֹבֶשֶׁת — אִין, אֲבָל חָרִיץ — לָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עָבְדָא? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תְּרֵי תַנָּאֵי, וְאַלִּיבָּא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">דְּרַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"122\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><br><br><big><strong>הֲדַרַן עֲלָךְ יוֹם טוֹב</strong></big><br><br>",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"110\" data-sentence-id=\"10\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"א\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"10\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>אֵין צָדִין</strong></big> דָּגִים מִן הַבִּיבָרִים בְּיוֹם טוֹב, וְאֵין נוֹתְנִין",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לִפְנֵיהֶם מְזוֹנוֹת. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"11\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֲבָל צָדִין חַיָּה וְעוֹף מִן",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַבִּיבָרִין, וְנוֹתְנִין לִפְנֵיהֶם מְזוֹנוֹת. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"12\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabban Shimon ben Gamliel II, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2852\" data-full-name=\"Rabban Shimon ben Gamliel II\" data-name-he=\"רבן שמעון בן גמליאל\">רַבָּן שִׁמְעוֹן בֶּן גַּמְלִיאֵל</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        12
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹמֵר: לֹא כָּל הַבִּיבָרִין שָׁוִין. זֶה הַכְּלָל: כׇּל",
      "segment_ids": [
        12
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">מתני&#x27;</span> טְמֵאָה מִשּׁוּם שְׁלֹשָׁה כֵּלִים.</b> מקבלת טומאה על שם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שלשה כלים נפקא מינה דאי נמי אזל חד שמא מינה טמאה משום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אידך ובגמרא מפרש לה: <b>גְּמָ׳ תַּחְתּוֹנָה</b> שמקבלת אבק הפלפלין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כשנופל דרך נקבי המכבר: <b>מִשּׁוּם כְּלִי קִבּוּל</b> שכלי עץ שיש לו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בית קבול הוא: <b>אֶמְצָעִית.</b> שהיא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מקפת את המכבר משום כלי עץ",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לא מטמאה דאין קבולה קבול אלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "חכמים גזרו טומאה על הכברה משום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ארוג ואפי' אין המכבר של מתכת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מטמאה משום כלי כברה ושלנו שהיא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "של מתכת ודאי טמאה משום פשוטי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כלי מתכות: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ועליונה</span>.</b> שמכתשין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ושוחקין בה הפלפלין טמאה משום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כלי מתכות דמשום כלי עץ ליכא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לטמויה דפשוטיהן טהורין אלא משום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "צפוי התחתון שהוא עיקר והעץ בטל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אצלו: <b>מַתְנִי׳ עֲגָלָה שֶׁל קָטָן.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שעושין לו לשחוק ויושב עליה ומטלטלין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אותו עליה: <b>טְמֵאָה מִדְרָס.</b> אם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "התינוק זב נעשית העגלה אב הטומאה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דמיוחדת לישיבה היא דהא סומך קטן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "עליה נמצאת שהיא מיוחדת לו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לישיבה ואין אומרים לו עמוד ונעשה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מלאכתנו דאילו לא מיחדא להכי לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הות אב הטומאה כדתניא יכול כפה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "סאה וישב עליה כו' (<a href=\"/shabbat/59a\">שבת דף נט.</a>):",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>וְנִטֶּלֶת בְּשַׁבָּת</b> דתורת כלי עליה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>וְאֵינָהּ נִגְרֶרֶת</b> בשבת: <b>אלא</b> <b>על</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>גַּבֵּי כֵלִים.</b> על גבי בגדים מפני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שעושה חריץ בקרקע וחופר חייב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:3:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "משום חורש: <b>מִפְּנֵי שֶׁכּוֹבֶשֶׁת.</b> חריץ",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הנראה בהלוכה לא על ידי חפירה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הוא אלא כובשת ודורסת הקרקע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ונדוש תחתיה ונעשה מקומה נמוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אבל אינו זז עפר ממקומה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "גמ' לעשות חריץ גרסינן: <b>כּוֹבֶשֶׁת</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>אֵין</b> כובשת הוי אבל חריץ לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:11:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "עבדא: <b>תְּרֵי תַנָּאֵי, וְאַלִּיבָּא דְּרַבִּי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:11:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>יְהוּדָה.</b> חד סבר העגלה נמי כשאר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:11:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כלים דעושה חריץ בגרירתה שפעמים שאין האופן מתגלגל והוא נגרר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:11:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וחופר ואידך סבר לא שכיח הכי ואינה אלא כובשת תחת גלגולה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:11:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>אין צדין דגים.</b> אף על גב דשחיטה ואפייה ובשול מאבות מלאכות"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הן והותרו לצורך יום טוב טעמא משום דאי אפשר מערב"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "יום טוב דשחיטה חייש למכמר בשרא פן יתחמם ויסריח אבל"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "צידה אפשר לצודו מבעוד יום ויניחנו במצודתו במים ולא ימות"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ולמחר יטלהו: <b>ביברים.</b> של דגים הן בריכות של מים שקורין ויביי\"ר"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ביברין של חיה קרפיפות מוקפין גדר סביב וכונסין לתוכן חיות"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הבר ויולדות ומגדלות שם: <b>ואין נותנין.</b> לפני הדגים מזונות"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ואפי' למאן דאמר נפש בהמה במשמע הני מילי דמזונותן עליך"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אבל דגים אפשר להם בלא מזונות שהם אוכלים שרשי עשבים"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וקרקע וגדול אוכל את הקטן: <b>אֲבָל צָדִין חַיָּה וְעוֹף.</b> המכונסים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:12:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מאתמול קא סלקא דעתך השתא כיון דמוקפים גדר הוו להו כנצודין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:12:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ועומדין אבל דגים נשמטין לחורים ולסדקים והויא צידה ביום טוב:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:12:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>וְנוֹתְנִין לִפְנֵיהֶם מְזוֹנוֹת.</b> בימי החורף צריכין מזונות ואף בימי הקיץ",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:12:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "במקום דריסת בני אדם שאין עשבים עולים בו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 23b:12:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    }
  ],
  "vilna_piskaot": [
    {
      "id": 119,
      "symbol": "׃",
